<li id="cite_note-7"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-7">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Brown&#160;<a href="#CITEREFBrown1991">1991</a>, Theorem I.2.24</span></li>
