<li id="cite_note-9"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-9">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Brown&#160;<a href="#CITEREFBrown1991">1991</a>, I.2.21 and 22</span></li>
